with my friend:</p>
<p>Alison: You absolutely need to maintain continuity of treatment.</p>
<p> Colleague: But what if that violates State regulations?</p>
<p> Alison: You canâ€™t think about that at a time like this. I canâ€™t 
imagine the State will come down on you for maintaining continuity of 
